('314-301.jpg', NULL, 'Grottes des Planches', 'Dry Upper Level', '', 'This upper level of the cave is now dry.\r\nStill it shows all the typical features of a young river cave.\r\nUntil now no speleothems have been formed.\r\nA hard, nearly horizontal layer of limestone forms the ceiling, which gives the passage a triangular shape.', '', 'Jochen Duckeck', NULL, NULL, NULL),
