('159-205.jpg', NULL, 'Cheddar Gorge', 'A Nameless Cave', '', 'Of course, this cave is not nameless. We just don’t know it. You will find it if you drive through Cheddar Gorge on the southern side of the valley. It is pretty easy to enter, and with a torch you may follow the main passage for a few Meters. But be carefull: after about 10m is a dangerous drop!', '', 'Jochen Duckeck', '', '', ''),
