('D056-0831.jpg', NULL, '&#931;&#960;&#951;&#955;&#945;&#953;&#959; &#932;&#969;&#957; &#923;&#953;&#956;&#957;&#969;&#957;', 'The Karst Plain Above the Ton Limnon Cave', '', 'This plain above the cave Ton Limnon, between Kastria and Kato Lousi, is composed of karstified limestone. There is no subaerial water here, and the plain ist rather dry.\r\nAll water is flowing underground, in the lowest cave level of Ton Limnon.\r\nOnly during heavy rains it rises and reaches the show cave.', '', 'Jochen Duckeck', '', '', ''),
