('043-171.jpg', NULL, 'The Burren', 'Bare Karst in the Mist', '', 'The Burren is a bare  karst area in the west of Ireland.\r\nThe central burren is sparsely populated and there is only one road going through.\r\nBetween the rocks is only some grass, there are no bushes and no trees.\r\nBut this landscape is influenced by man and his sheep.', '', 'Jochen Duckeck', '', '', ''),
